  "text": "and (x k+1 , s k+1 ) = (x k , s k )) otherwise. Note that δ f k > 0 (because of [CITATION_1] and (29)) unless (x k , s k ) is first-order critical, and hence that condition (35) is well-defined. As for the value of the funnel bound, we set v max k+1 = v max k .",
